l=https://tw.movies.yahoo.com/spotlight/articles/150311/21072341-79c0-393e-aa9b-f806fe9dd3ef/%E5%86%B0%E9%9B%AA%E5%A5%87%E7%B7%A3-%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E6%90%AD%E6%AA%94-%E7%BA%8C%E9%9B%86%E6%9A%AB%E7%84%A1%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-035826180.html |date=20150401214935 }}. Yahoo!奇摩電影. 2015-03-11.</ref>。儘管種種否認，迪士尼終在2015年3月12日所舉辦年度[[股東大會|股東大會]]上，宣佈《冰雪奇缘2》（''Frozen 2''）的計劃<ref>[https://d23.com/walt-disney-company-announces-plans-new-star-wars-films/ The Walt Disney Company Announces Plans for Frozen 2, New Star Wars Films] {{Wayback|url=https://d23.com/walt-disney-company-announces-plans-new-star-wars-films/ |date=20150315044512 }}, D23.com, 2015-03-12.</ref><ref>{{Twitter status|IMKristenBell|576083794471620608|Dreams really do come 2!!!|Kristen Bell|2015-03-12.| | }}</ref><ref>{{Twitter status|alittlejelee|576078755015200769|At last, I can say - FROZEN 2!!!!|Jennifer Lee|2015-03-12.| | }}</ref>。

